general.name: photo2MASSCamcol
general.description: Contains matches of the SDSS imaging data to the 2MASS Point Source Catalog, for a single field. Identification information for the SDSS source is given, along with all of the 2MASS information. See the official 2MASS documentation for detailed documentation of the 2MASS formats. These matches are to any objects which are RUN_PRIMARY according to the local resolve (see resolve documentation ). See individual field files for full description.
